{
  "stem": "1901.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I sit down, you know, nicely on the side there until there were another 10, 15, 20 in, and then another 20 in, and another 20 in, and another 20 in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we have to stand up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't sit anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then end of the story, we're standing like this. 130-- this documented.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know more about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were at 130 men in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the train start rolling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were some open wagons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had a closed wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's good for six horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was written on it, six [NON-ENGLISH], it was written on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know what room is six horses-- 130 men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we start rolling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we did that for six days and seven nights [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] till we arrived in-- the train goes backwards and forwards, backwards and forwards, and backwards.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, after one day, there was a little bit more room because the people start dying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We lay them down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Dachau, there were 29 left of the 130.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were sitting right on top-- right on top of the bodies, because everyone who died, down, we laid them down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we sit on top of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Filthy, dirty, the toilets, you know, they-- we ripped clothes off-- the smell-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] must have been something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It must have been a sight for us, how we looked like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I didn't look at myself in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I saw the other ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one fellow who I spoke to, he was as flat as a pancake, because everything-- he rips, everything goes cracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you stand on it, and lay on it, with no-- and you put them up.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
